Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:49.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}任何人都在迷茫中寻觅答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.11,0:01:09.49,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}曾以为二人同心　时间也可支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:17.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}当岁月流逝　天空不再湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心与心渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:30.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}周而复始　季节循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:36.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}愿时光　永远停留在那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:43.13,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}二人仍迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:52.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在天边寻找各自真爱的岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉是我未来的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开驾驶舱！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是在被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他父母是自然人 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与之战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:16.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}和平的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别编号 285002
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽队所属 阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经预约与拉克丝小姐会面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认完毕 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍许来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这群哈罗怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在欢迎客人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…它们这样不碍事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是你所以才这么高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你上次来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍加狓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把花带去 给阿里先生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 麻烦他沏杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小海蓝 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 元气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你是胡子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 有胡子的是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 未能赶回参加追悼仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经代你 向令母大人祈祷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你已经回国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直期待与你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次会多待一段时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假的日程终归只是暂定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近参军的人 听说又增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的好几位朋友也志愿参加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉战争在日渐扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实情况就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 不知道基拉先生现在如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之后 你们见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能在地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们从小就是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从4，5岁起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前住在月球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行将开战前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被父亲先一步带回PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明也说会来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把哈罗的事告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说你一点也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得别提多高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己的特利也是你给做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉先生很宝贝它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还带着那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好几次看见停在他肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 它叫特利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是 我的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 喜欢那位先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非主张占领地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续扩大战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 情况如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也必须采取相应措施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声称中立的奥布赫利奥波利斯的背叛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它们 坚持对话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成为一桩不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持反对的克莱茵令人无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你驾驶的那架…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫迅雷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了机体构造资料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人看了都会有危机感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视 关
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骤雨作战计划的通过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们须尽可能减少浪费在战争上的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽队长也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决议一旦通过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又得上前线去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些自己想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你父亲下楼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人们看这些就会获得支持吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民需要知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你挑选出的真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的提案 骤雨作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就会被通过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舆论一旦形成 将无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制度代表的是全体意志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要忘记这点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战火扩大意味着不可调和的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们究竟想去往何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此也必须早期结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争必须获胜才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们调整人已经是一种新的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须与自然人进行调和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经面临繁衍危机的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里称得上新种群？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便实施强制婚姻政策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代出生率一降再降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今为止也绝非一片坦途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题天生就是要被克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的睿智下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕德里克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命是孕育而生的 非人造之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才应该明白 这种概念与价值观已经落伍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人必须前行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远为了追寻更好的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那样才能幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉委员长 时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请来议事厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现有制度下的人们的共同意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经无法抛弃获得的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进化途中折返做回自然人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不是进化的产物 帕德里克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 对最高议会议案进行评议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各议员在充分议论后作出裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议案一 关于骤雨作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉委员长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该还是评议会的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议案已经通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两三项小议案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束后 晚上与你详谈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我会来找您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 我们只要动真格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管狂妄吧 帕德里克·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了 我全以为你会留下进晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议会结束后父亲也会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一直说想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情实在堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…可能短期内很难有空造访
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…有时间我一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰看起来好忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 哈罗 不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好几次看见停在他肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不可能了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉别露面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开了躲在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得又吵起来 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是纪律 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里地下全是废矿坑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有我们布的地雷阵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场就选这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手肯定也会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费力布的地雷不用多可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的打算干？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的装备水平 损失会很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从老虎 在他手下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他干活的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实能过上平和的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像巴堤雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人里也有人希望那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 支配者的心情多变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们族人为此受了几百年苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被支配也不去支配
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要夺回被老虎控制的东面工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想或许就能成真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就指望你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的不用操心 我们会照顾好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们乐意接受贵方协助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实施突破莱塞普号的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多尔快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫卡嘉莉来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有实战经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打中了两发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚上战场就被击落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么 大家都试过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些当兵的太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说枪也没开过？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在打仗 打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 有什么好神气的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开过枪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为军人没开过枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么可神气的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会当作训练认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 被击落的话不准吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 这是真家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 你这是干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛的房间外 看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 好傻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不可能赢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真正的骤雨作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的议长竞选
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵的后任非阁下莫属
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当做万全准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次战斗时 我会向你开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法逃避 因为是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死我活 如此单纯的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁定下规则
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炙热的沙漠化作战场  令人无暇思考
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此的枪口 指向哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沙漠尽头」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣下扳机 高达







